# üêæ Pet Manager ‚Äî JavaFX Project

This is a JavaFX desktop application built as part of a Programming 2 assignment. It allows users to manage a collection of virtual pets, including creating, editing, deleting, and exporting/importing them from Excel files. The project emphasizes clean UI interaction, validation, and data persistence.

---

Features

- Add new pets with customizable happiness, hunger, and energy levels
- Search pets by name
- ‚úèEdit pets directly in the TableView
- Delete pets
- Export pets to Excel
- Import pets from Excel (while preserving pet IDs)
- Input validation with clear error handling
- Built using JavaFX and SceneBuilder

 Technologies 

- Java 17+
- JavaFX
- Apache POI (for Excel file handling)
- Maven (project build tool)
- IntelliJ IDEA (recommended IDE)

